				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Check your timing (nmi timing/'delay', sprite/apu dma cycles, additional cycles for branch taken/page crossing, etc.).  That said, my scanline-based ppu has the same issue, to a lesser degree (level 2 isn't as bad), my cycle-based ppu is fine.  If you're performing scanline-based emulation, you might not be able to get it to work without hacks.
<br />
<br />DMC IRQs don't matter for Battletoads (my emulator doesn't even support them).</div>

