				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If a sprite's Y coordinate in OAM is 239, its top visible pixel is below the visible area. The PPU fetches its OAM entries during line 260*, fetches its pattern slivers in the following hblank, and never actually displays these pattern slivers because line 261 is the post-render line.
<br />
<br /><span style="font-size: 84%; line-height: normal">* Assuming the visible scanlines are 21 through 260</span></div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

